---
interface Props {
  title: string;
  description?: string;
  ogImage?: string;
  canonical?: string;
}

const {
  title,
  description = "Descubre todas las deducciones del IRPF 2025 en segundos. Asistente interactivo + explorador con las 375 deducciones estatales y autonómicas.",
  ogImage = "/api/og?title=Tu+gu%C3%ADa+completa+del+IRPF",
  canonical,
} = Astro.props;

const siteUrl = "https://www.larenta.es";
const pageUrl = canonical || new URL(Astro.url.pathname, siteUrl).href;
const fullTitle = title === "larenta.es" ? title + " — Tu guía completa del IRPF 2025" : `${title} | larenta.es`;
const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <!-- SEO -->
    <title>{fullTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <link rel="canonical" href={pageUrl} />

    <!-- Open Graph -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={pageUrl} />
    <meta property="og:title" content={fullTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={new URL(ogImage, siteUrl).href} />
    <meta property="og:locale" content="es_ES" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="larenta.es" />

    <!-- Twitter -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={fullTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={description} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={new URL(ogImage, siteUrl).href} />

    <!-- Fonts: Public Sans (The Civic Ledger) -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Public+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,400&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style is:global>
      @import "../styles/global.css";
    </style>

    <!-- Google Tag Manager -->
    <script is:inline>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':
    new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],
    j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=
    'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);
    })(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-P5HKM4NQ');</script>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager -->

    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script is:inline async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-9BMRQTWEG5"></script>
    <script is:inline>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());
      gtag('config', 'G-9BMRQTWEG5');
    </script>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col" style="background: var(--color-surface);">
    <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-P5HKM4NQ"
    height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->

    <!-- Nav glassmorphic -->
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 glass" style="box-shadow: 0 1px 0 var(--color-outline-variant);">
      <nav class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <a href="/" class="group" aria-label="larenta.es - Inicio">
          <span class="text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color: var(--color-primary); letter-spacing: -0.04ch;">
            LARENTA<span style="color: var(--color-secondary); font-weight: 800;">.ES</span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <!-- Links de navegación -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
          <a
            href="/guia"
            class:list={["px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-xl transition-colors", 
              currentPath.startsWith('/guia') ? "text-[var(--color-primary)] bg-[var(--color-surface-high)]" : "text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-surface-high)]"
            ]}
          >
            Guía IRPF
          </a>
          <a
            href="/asistente"
            class:list={["px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-xl transition-colors",
              currentPath === '/asistente' ? "text-[var(--color-primary)] bg-[var(--color-surface-high)]" : "text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-surface-high)]"
            ]}
          >
            Asistente
          </a>
          <a
            href="/explorador"
            class:list={["px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-xl transition-colors",
              currentPath === '/explorador' ? "text-[var(--color-primary)] bg-[var(--color-surface-high)]" : "text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-surface-high)]"
            ]}
          >
            Deducciones
          </a>
          <a
            href="/asistente"
            class="btn-primary ml-2 !py-2 !px-4 !text-sm hidden sm:inline-flex"
          >
            Calcular mi renta
          </a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-1">
      <slot />
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style="background: var(--color-on-surface); color: var(--color-surface);">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-14">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
          <!-- Marca -->
          <div class="sm:col-span-2">
            <span class="text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.04ch;">
              LARENTA<span style="color: var(--color-secondary-container); font-weight: 800;">.ES</span>
            </span>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm max-w-xs leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(246,250,255,0.6);">
              Tu guía completa del IRPF 2025. Deducciones estatales y autonómicas explicadas de forma clara, con datos oficiales de la AEAT.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Herramientas -->
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-4" style="color: rgba(246,250,255,0.9);">Herramientas</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm" style="color: rgba(246,250,255,0.54);">
              <li><a href="/asistente" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Asistente interactivo</a></li>
              <li><a href="/explorador" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Explorador de deducciones</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guia" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Guía IRPF 2025</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Legal -->
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-4" style="color: rgba(246,250,255,0.9);">Fuentes y legal</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm" style="color: rgba(246,250,255,0.54);">
              <li>
                <a href="https://sede.agenciatributaria.gob.es" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  AEAT — Agencia Tributaria ↗
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="text-xs pt-1 leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(246,250,255,0.38);">
                Información orientativa. No constituye asesoramiento fiscal. Consulta siempre con un profesional.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom bar -->
        <div class="mt-10 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3 text-xs"
          style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(246,250,255,0.1); color: rgba(246,250,255,0.38);">
          <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} larenta.es</span>
          <span>Datos del Manual de la Renta 2025 — AEAT</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
